OK, True Confessions Time!  You know that once every three-month craving you get after you come from an artistic neighborhood venue where there was no food, you're starving, and you just happen to walk by a--wait a minute--is that--yup--Texas Fried Chicken--and order almost everything on the menu like you're at a restaurant because you're starving--and then you wonder will you feel guilty--and justify it all by saying HECK NO to yourself because you don't eat this that often anyways!  That is what Texas Chicken and Burgers (eventhough I've never had any burgers from there)  is good for!
